            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "And over that time, my alchemy skills have improved, and I've collected different flower specimens..."
